statements: SELECT * FROM BuildingOccupancy
SELECT building_id, occupancy_date FROM BuildingOccupancy ORDER BY occupancy_date DESC
SELECT MAX(occupancy_value) AS max_occupancy FROM BuildingOccupancy
SELECT * FROM BuildingOccupancy WHERE occupancy_date > '2022-01-01'
SELECT building_id, SUM(occupancy_value) AS total_occupancy FROM BuildingOccupancy GROUP BY building_id
SELECT * FROM BuildingOccupancy ORDER BY occupancy_date DESC, occupancy_value ASC
SELECT building_id, occupancy_date FROM BuildingOccupancy WHERE occupancy_value > 10
SELECT * FROM BuildingOccupancy WHERE building_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000'
SELECT DISTINCT occupancy_date FROM BuildingOccupancy
SELECT AVG(occupancy_value) AS average_occupancy FROM BuildingOccupancy
SELECT * FROM Green_Building_Projects;
SELECT building_name, occupancy_status FROM Green_Building_Projects WHERE occupancy_status = 'occupied';
SELECT building_name, occupancy_capacity, occupancy_count FROM Green_Building_Projects ORDER BY occupancy_count DESC;
SELECT room_name, occupant_name, check_in_time FROM Room_Occupancy WHERE check_in_time >= '2022-01-01';

SELECT building_name, room_name, occupant_name, check_out_time FROM Green_Building_Projects JOIN Room_Occupancy ON Green_Building_Projects.building_id = Room_Occupancy.building_id WHERE occupancy_status = 'occupied';
SELECT building_id, building_name, occupancy_status FROM Green_Building_Projects
SELECT DISTINCT building_name, occupancy_capacity FROM Green_Building_Projects ORDER BY occupancy_capacity DESC
SELECT building_name, occupancy_capacity, occupancy_count FROM Green_Building_Projects WHERE occupancy_capacity > occupancy_count
SELECT * FROM Room_Occupancy WHERE check_out_time IS NULL ORDER BY check_in_time DESC
SELECT room_name, occupant_name, check_in_time, check_out_time FROM Room_Occupancy WHERE occupancy_status = 'occupied' AND check_out_time < CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
SELECT * FROM building_occupancy;
SELECT building_id, occupancy_date, number_of_occupants FROM building_occupancy WHERE number_of_occupants > 50;
SELECT building_id, type_name FROM building_occupancy bo JOIN occupancy_type ot ON bo.building_id = ot.type_id;
SELECT * FROM space_utilization ORDER BY occupancy_percentage DESC;
SELECT building_id, SUM(occupancy_percentage) AS total_utilization FROM space_utilization GROUP BY building_id;
SELECT * FROM building_occupancy WHERE building_id = 1;
SELECT type_name, type_id FROM occupancy_type ORDER BY type_name DESC;
SELECT occupancy_id, building_id, type_id, occupancy_percentage FROM space_utilization WHERE occupancy_percentage > 50;
SELECT DISTINCT building_id FROM building_occupancy ORDER BY occupancy_date DESC, occupancy_time ASC;
SELECT building_id, SUM(number_of_occupants) AS total_occupants FROM building_occupancy GROUP BY building_id HAVING total_occupants > 100;
SELECT * FROM Building_Information;
SELECT building_name, total_floors FROM Building_Information ORDER BY building_name DESC;
SELECT building_id, building_address FROM Building_Information WHERE total_floors > 5;
SELECT * FROM Occupancy_Data WHERE floor_number = 3 AND occupancy_status = 'Occupied';
SELECT building_name, consumption FROM Building_Information INNER JOIN Energy_Consumption ON Building_Information.building_id = Energy_Consumption.building_id;
SELECT * FROM Building_Information WHERE total_floors > 5;
SELECT building_name, building_address FROM Building_Information WHERE building_id = 3;

SELECT b.building_name, o.floor_number, s.area_used FROM Building_Information b JOIN Occupancy_Data o ON b.building_id = o.building_id JOIN Space_Utilization s ON o.occupancy_id = s.occupancy_id WHERE s.utilization_rate > 80;
SELECT e.building_id, e.energy_type, SUM(e.consumption) AS total_consumption FROM Energy_Consumption e JOIN Building_Information b ON e.building_id = b.building_id GROUP BY e.building_id;

SELECT b.building_name, o.floor_number, e.energy_type, e.consumption FROM Building_Information b JOIN Occupancy_Data o ON b.building_id = o.building_id JOIN Energy_Consumption e ON b.building_id = e.building_id WHERE e.consumption > 100;
SELECT * FROM Building;
SELECT building_name, building_location FROM Building ORDER BY building_location DESC;
SELECT room_name, room_area FROM Room WHERE room_area > 100 ORDER BY room_area ASC;
SELECT building_name, total_floors FROM Building WHERE total_floors >= 5;
SELECT occupant_name, start_date, end_date FROM Occupancy WHERE start_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT * FROM Building;
SELECT building_name, total_floors FROM Building WHERE total_floors > 5;
SELECT room_name, room_area, Floor.floor_number FROM Room JOIN Floor ON Room.floor_id = Floor.floor_id WHERE Room.room_area > 50;
SELECT room_name, occupant_name, Occupancy.start_date, Occupancy.end_date FROM Room JOIN Occupancy ON Room.room_id = Occupancy.room_id WHERE occupant_name LIKE 'John%';

SELECT Building.building_name, Floor.floor_number, Utilization_Report.total_occupants FROM Building JOIN Floor ON Building.building_id = Floor.building_id JOIN Utilization_Report ON Building.building_id = Utilization_Report.building_id AND Floor.floor_id = Utilization_Report.floor_id WHERE Utilization_Report.total_occupants > 10;
